%description
XMMS Output Plugin for Crossfading and Continuous Output

Features:
  * Crossfading
  * Continuous output
  * Gap-Killer: Some mp3-encoders produce small gaps of silence at the
    beginning or end of the stream. They can automatically be detected
    and removed.

